In re Resignation of Berger.

[Cite as In re Resignation of Berger (1990), 51 Ohio St. 3d 602.]

(No. 90-594 Submitted April 17, 1990 Decided May 2, 1990.)

The resignation of Peter S. Berger as an attorney is accepted.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Holmes, Douglas, Wright, H. Brown and Resnick, JJ., concur.
